{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_01","textHome":"其实我呀，是最近才知道@自己有着时女一族的血统的。@毕竟，连以前应该听外婆提过的妈妈@都没记得这回事，那我不知道也不奇怪了。@然后呀，我现在很激动哦。@因为我终于，得到了能帮助大家的机会！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_17","textHome":"果然刑事或者侦探剧最精彩的地方@就在于每话完结之处！@并非为了让人在意后续，@而是让人感到“哇，看完啦——！”"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_18","textHome":"要说当英雄的梦想，果然还是要解决大事件，@被后世传颂，拍成电影！比如鼠小僧这样的！@……啊，那个是坏人！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":400}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_19","textHome":"我的鼻子现在很痛，@也就是闻到了案件的气息！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_20","textHome":"我的人生动起来了！@向着英雄加速迈步吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_21","textHome":"完成了使命我便能成为英雄。@但是，成为英雄并不是目的。@改变时女一族才是目的。@现在可不能停下！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":0}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_22","textHome":"身负魔法少女的命运，生命可能会很短暂……@但是我们有着在此之上的牢固牵绊！@绝不会输给什么命运！人生苦短呀少女！@我会和静香还有沙绪一起加油的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":8.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_23","textHome":"老旧的袜子或者裤子口袋这些，@线一旦开始松掉就会渐渐全部解开。@我们的关系也是那种感觉。@看来是在哪里出现了薄弱的地方呢……@不过我不会放弃。现在的话一定能够修复的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_031.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_50_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102650,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_50_25"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"id":102650,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102650,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_50_26"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":102650,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_00_02","textHome":"初次见面，我是时女一族的广江千春！@下次有机会的话可以跟我一起巡逻吗？@我呀，很喜欢晃晃悠悠地散步"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102600}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102650,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1026_50_27"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102650}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":102650,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102650,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id